Localization.Name: Gyson Inc.
Localization.Description: If you need it, Gyson makes it. The company and its subsidiaries produce everything from carpets to cleaning solvents to industrial uniforms and even EVA suits at prices that can't be beat.

Localization.Name: J-5 Helmet Pyrotechnic
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Light Helmet
Damage Reduction: 20%
Temp. Rating: -25 / 65 °C
Radiation Protection: 15200 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 81 REM/s

Gyson delivers another unique softshell helmet with the J-5. Large optic sensors and an oversized breathing apparatus deliver a striking visage. The distinct design is space-rated and provides a modicum of protection, while keeping the helmet lightweight and affordable. This edition features the colors and logo of the now defunct Pyrotechnic Amalgamated.
